# ====================================================================
# GlowChess - Git Ignore File (.gitignore)
# ====================================================================
# Under industry-standard security guidelines, this file ensures that:
# 1. Local environment secrets (.env) are NEVER pushed to GitHub.
# 2. Local OS cache files (.DS_Store) and compiler outputs are kept out of source control.
# 3. Third-party dependencies (node_modules) are ignored, since they are rebuilt in CI/CD.
# ====================================================================

# Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp
.pnp.js

# Production Build Output (Vercel builds this on the fly)
dist/
build/

# Local Environment Variables & Secrets
# WARNING: NEVER REMOVE THIS! Pushing .env files to GitHub leaks private keys.
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# Debug logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Operating System Files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
